lektor for Debian
------------------

Configuration
-------------

The example configuration file is installed at:
  /usr/share/lektor/config.example.toml

To use it, copy it to your home directory:
  mkdir -p ~/.config/lektor
  cp /usr/share/lektor/config.example.toml ~/.config/lektor/config.toml

Then edit ~/.config/lektor/config.toml to customize lektor to your preferences.

Documentation
-------------

Additional documentation can be found at:
  /usr/share/doc/lektor/

Building from Source
--------------------

If you want to rebuild this package from source:

1. Install build dependencies:
   sudo apt-get build-dep lektor

2. Build the package:
   dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc -b

Or use the provided Makefile:
   make deb

